! &#124; British Board of Film Classification|website=bbfc.co.uk}}</ref> || Rohini Baxi ||\n|-\n| ''[[Bichhoo]]'' || Jeeva's mom ||\n|-\n| ''[[Tera Jadoo Chal Gayaa]]'' || Pooja's mother ||\n|-\n| ''[[Gaja Gamini]]'' || Noorbibi ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"|2001 || [[Farz (2001 film)|''Farz'']] || Rukmani Singh ||\n|-\n| ''[[Zubeidaa]]'' || Mammo ||\n|-\n| ''[[Chori Chori Chupke Chupke]]'' || Asha Malhotra ||\n|-\n| [[Lajja (2001 film)|''Lajja'']] || Mother of Bride ||\n|-\n| ''[[Moksha: Salvation]]'' || Salim's mother ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham...]]'' || Sayeeda/Daijan/DJ ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|2002 || ''[[Pyaar Diwana Hota Hai]]'' || Mrs. Chaudhary ||\n|-\n| ''[[The Legend of Bhagat Singh]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/bhagat-singh-films/216170/__LINK__|title=Bhagat Singh Films &#124; Outlook India Magazine|website=https://www.outlookindia.com/}}</ref> || Vidyavati ||\n|-\n| ''[[Badhaai Ho Badhaai]]'' || Mrs. Chaddha ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kuch Tum Kaho Kuch Hum Kahein]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rediff.com/movies/2002/jun/13sld1.htm|title=rediff.com, Movies: Kuch Tum Kaho Kuch Hum Kahein: Story in Pictures|website=www.rediff.com}}</ref> || Vishnupratap's wife ||\n|-\n| ''[[Deewangee]]'' || Mrs. Goyal ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\"|2003 || [[Pinjar (film)|''Pinjar'']] || Mrs. Shyamlal ||\n|-\n| ''[[Aapko Pehle Bhi Kahin Dekha Hai]]'' || Jiji ||\n|-\n| ''[[Kaise Kahoon Ke... Pyaar Hai]]'' || ||\n|-\n| ''[[Main Prem Ki Diwani Hoon]]'' || Mrs. Kapoor ||\n|-\n| ''[[Jaal: The Trap]]'' || Sudha Kaul ||\n|-\n| ''[[Fun 2shh: Dudes In the 10th Century]]'' || Mrs. DiSouza/Hiraka ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2004 || ''[[Garv: Pride and Honour]]'' || Mrs. Shakuntala Dixit ||\n|-\n| ''[[Taarzan: The Wonder Car]]'' || Mrs. Chaudhary<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sify.com/movies/taarzan-the-wonder-car-review-bollywood-pclv5lhaggeeh.html|title=Taarzan The Wonder Car|website=Sify}}</ref> ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2005 || ''[[Pyaar Mein Twist]]'' || Ms.